    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's a lot more than just \"focus\" though. it feels structural. like my neurons are firing at a higher frequency. i was reading about how cosmic radiation can cause micro-mutations in DNA, and i can't help but feel like that's what happened. like my genetic code actually received an update during those flares. if you look at the data on geomagnetic storms, isn't it possible they could trigger rapid epigenetic changes in humans?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
