      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it feels deeper than just \"turning genes on or off.\" it feels like the actual blueprints are changing. i'm starting to see patterns in things i never noticed before, like seeing the mathematical structure in everyday objects. if the radiation actually caused a localized mutation in my germline or even somatic cells, couldn't that explain why i feel like i'm literally becoming a different version of myself? like, can't you see how the timing with the solar activity makes it more than just a coincidence?",
